1.0.1.name: wordpress/dandyid-services
1.0.1.description:
DandyID is a free service that enables you to connect, manage, and share all of your online identities from a single location.

The DandyID Services Plugin:

  • Retrieves all of your DandyID online identities.
  • Displays them as clickable links in your blog sidebar.
  • Please see the Screenshots for examples.

When you update your identities on DandyID, they are automatically updated in your sidebar.

DandyID currently supports over 300 services including:

  • 12seconds
  • 30 Boxes
  • 43marks
  • 43 People
  • 43 Places
  • 43 Things
  • 97 Bottles
  • ActiveRain
  • Adocu
  • AgencyScoop
  • AIM
  • All Consuming
  • Amazon
  • Amazon Wish List
  • Amie St

DandyID is a free service that enables you to connect, manage, and share all of your online identities from a single location.

The DandyID Services Plugin:

  • Retrieves all of your DandyID online identities.
  • Displays them as clickable links in your blog sidebar.
  • Please see the Screenshots for examples.

When you update your identities on DandyID, they are automatically updated in your sidebar.

DandyID currently supports over 300 services including:

  • 12seconds
  • 30 Boxes
  • 43marks
  • 43 People
  • 43 Places
  • 43 Things
  • 97 Bottles
  • ActiveRain
  • Adocu
  • AgencyScoop
  • AIM
  • All Consuming
  • Amazon
  • Amazon Wish List
  • Amie St
